1. User downloads torrent file from his tracker.
2. Opens downloaded torrent file in the bittorrent client.
3. Set final parameters for downloading data:
  a) a single-file torrent: the location and the name of the file;
  b) a multi-file torrent: the location and name of the directory, chosen for download files and their names, names of intermediate directories.
4. The bittorrent starts downloading torrent content.
5. When the torrent content is downloaded the bittorrent client continues seeding the torrent content.